name: JuiceBoxJungle
overview: JuiceBoxJungle’s programs offer spirited commentary, expert views, honest confessions from parents, and quirky humor – and offer you the opportunity to become part of the conversation! Moderated by two former HBO execs and moms Melissa and Philippa, the programs tackle fun and edgy parenting topics (for a list, see bottom of page) on a range of issues you care about – from “Daddy Doesn’t Do it Right” to “You’re Not So Special” – with a spicy, fun attitude that allows you to take a step back and realize that parenting these days is frankly a little nuts. With JuiceBoxJungle.com you’ll have the opportunity to hear what others Moms think, tell us what YOU think, and also read the best articles pulled from across the web on this very topic. Watch, read, and then contribute your ideas to the community-wide conversation that is happening everywhere, from blogs, parenting sites and social networks, to nights out with your friends and date night.
